tspan.tspan: The Pirate Party is a technology-oriented political society, driven
by the belief that civil liberties and personal freedoms should take
precedence over private and corporate interests. We embrace the
ideals of free culture and unrestricted access to information. The
society strives to preserve personal privacy and oppose
censorship and surveillance. We manage the Trinity VPN, which
helps students overcome internet censorship. The Pirate Party
also organises regular Hackathons, CTFs (Capture the Flag), and
seminars on Ethical Hacking, Privacy, and Cyber-Security.
